//   1. #[tool_router] generates `tool_router()` fn
//   2. #[tool_handler(router = self.tool_router)] wires list_tools + call_tool dispatch into ServerHandler
//   3. Without #[tool_handler]: list_tools() returns empty, call_tool() returns -32601
//   4. Keep server alive: svc.waiting().await (NOT let _ = serve(...))
//   5. ToolRouter<Self> field MUST exist on the struct
//   6. Implementation is #[non_exhaustive] — use Implementation::new() not struct literal
//   7. Error type is rmcp::ErrorData (aliased as McpError), NOT rmcp::model::ServerError
//   8. Tool params use `Parameters(params): Parameters<T>` destructuring pattern
//      (import `wrapper::Parameters` from rmcp; do NOT use the old aggr attribute)
//   9. schemars must be "1" (rmcp 1.3.0 depends on schemars 1.2.x)
//  10. rmcp features must include "transport-io" for stdio() to work
// ==============================================================================

